- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a generative latent variable model for learning multilingual word representations. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning and natural language processing. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper may involve neural network models for learning multilingual embeddings. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly mention any computer vision tasks, but it is possible that the proposed model may be applied to image-related tasks.
